    = ő†Őā-unstraight-cod'‚ČÉő†Őā-unstraight-cod ._‚ČÉ_.fwd

  ő†Őā-unstraight-cod‚Üźpullback
    : Pullback (precomp-ő† Y f) (postcomp-ő† (őĽ a ‚Üí g (f a)))
    ‚Üí ő†Őā-unstraight-cod f g
  ő†Őā-unstraight-cod‚Üźpullback
    = ő†Őā-unstraight-cod‚Üźő†Őā-unstraight-cod' ‚ąė ő†Őā-unstraight-cod'‚Üźpullback

