    : Arrow-ő† f g ‚Üí ő†Őā-unstraight-cod'
  ő†Őā-unstraight-cod'‚ÜźArrow-ő† (mk-amap j i H)
    = i
    , őĽ where b (a , refl) ‚Üí j a , H a

  ő†Őā-unstraight-cod'‚ÜźArrow-ő†-via-pullback
    : Arrow-ő† f g ‚Üí ő†Őā-unstraight-cod'
  ő†Őā-unstraight-cod'‚ÜźArrow-ő†-via-pullback
    = ő†Őā-unstraight-cod'‚Üźpullback ‚ąė Arrow-ő†‚ČÉpullback ._‚ČÉ_.fwd

