    : ő†Őā-unstraight-cod'‚ÜźArrow-ő†-via-pullback ~ ő†Őā-unstraight-cod'‚ÜźArrow-ő†
  ő†Őā-unstraight-cod'‚ÜźArrow-ő†~via-pullback (mk-amap j i H)
    = ő£-path‚Üí
        ( refl
        , funext‚Üí őĽ b ‚Üí funext‚Üí őĽ where
